<item>
            <title>[CASSANDRA-4256] Include stress tool in debian packaging</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-4256</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The stress tool isn&apos;t included in the debian packaging. We need to update that to grab the stress shell script as well as put the stress.jar file in lib.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also the stress shell script needs to be updated to include looking in /usr/share/cassandra... when searching for the stress jar so it will run in packaged installations.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12556269">CASSANDRA-4256</key>
            <summary>Include stress tool in debian packaging</summary>
